CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 20, reads: "Cecelia Trower passes out free shopping bags from the Trower's Cleaners and Shirt Laundry booth."
TitMainTitle: Cecelia Trower (Epperson) wearing pocket watch patterned dress, handing out paper shopping bags to women gathered around Trower Cleaners booth at the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair in Syria Mosque
